Introduction

HANA (Korean: 하나; Japanese: ハナ) was a South Korean girl group. They made their debut on January 8, 2023 with the single "BLA:ZE". On January 3, 2024, on HANA's official Instagram page, a photo with the members was posted, with a caption mentioning that the group's activities have ended, after careful consideration and discussion with the members, a decision has been made to permanently suspend group activities.
